# Never commit secrets or private state
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
secrets/
state/

# Never commit a real memory dir (only the template under memory-system/ is public)
memory/
**/MEMORY.md
!memory-system/MEMORY.template.md

# Backups and editor cruft
*.bak
*.bak-*
*~
.DS_Store

# Logs and telemetry
*.log
*.jsonl
